    LocDescriptions:
    - _name: FR
      Language: 0
      Txt: "<color=purple>Condition : \xE0 \xE9quiper uniquement sur des unit\xE9s
        dont la capacit\xE9 de combat au contact est <sprite name=die1> / figurine
        ou <sprite name=die1>.</color>\nAjoute 2 <sprite name=die2> suppl\xE9mentaires
        lorsque ton unit\xE9 attaque au contact."
    - _name: EN
      Language: 1
      Txt: 'When you attack in melee range, add 2 dice. If you split your attack
        between many targets with this gear, you may split these additional as you
        wish between the attacks.


        /!\ Only for units with only 1 die per
        miniature in melee range.'
